# dbt Snowflake Project

## Overview
dbt project connected to Snowflake salesdb.
Built following Zoltan C. Toth's Complete dbt Bootcamp.

## Tech Stack
- dbt Core
- Snowflake
- Python / uv

## Setup
1. Install uv
2. Create virtual environment
3. Install dbt-snowflake
4. Configure profiles.yml with your Snowflake credentials
5. Run dbt debug to verify connection

